commit message:
Don't use software rendering for webview on Marshmallow

Freezing issue seems to be fixed for Android 6.0

See https://code.google.com/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=501901
Inject feed color using javascript into the webview

Improve favicon handling

* Don't precache favicon, load on demand
* Restore default feed icon before starting to fetch favicon
* Get default feed icon in Fragment, not for each ViewHolder
Also reset default text color before loading the favicon
Fix initial sync, use -1 as offest to get all articles
Ignore warning about missing Google App Indexing support

Fix some lint warnings

Remove allowBackup again, conflicts with realm which has it set to true,
see https://github.com/realm/realm-java/issues/2227
